WHEN I make grapql call using the following query:
"""query GetArticle($forgeLocale: Language, $formatString: StringFormatDirectiveTypes, $storySlug: String!) {
  story: getArticle(slug: $storySlug, language: $forgeLocale) {   
    byline   
    contributors {
      name
      tagline(formatString: $formatString)      
      twitterHandle
    }
    headline   
    storyType: contentType
    summary
    tagline(formatString: $formatString)
    type
    title
  }
}"""

